One day he'll come again,

263
00:21:50,041 --> 00:21:51,791
so let's not get
too comfortable.

264
00:21:54,833 --> 00:21:58,000
[FAVARO]
Still alive. Just like me.

265
00:22:05,333 --> 00:22:08,291
You know which way that
wind is blowing, Favaro?

266
00:22:08,375 --> 00:22:10,041
Toward tomorrow!

267
00:23:09,958 --> 00:23:11,583
[KAISAR]
Favaro!

268
00:23:11,666 --> 00:23:13,375
[FAVARO]
Uh--

269
00:23:13,458 --> 00:23:16,416
